						<div class="postbody">Misinterpreted documentation would make sense, there are similar cases for the APU, like in Ikari Warriors II, which plays RAW via $4011 but still sets up and starts the DPCM unit like during normal 1-bit delta playback. Or take some Capcom games that write $30 to $400C and then also a $07 to $4015, as if you had to make doubly sure to silence the noise channel.</div>

